title: First Encounter Assault Recon (F.E.A.R.) v1.08
description:
First Encounter Assault Recon (F.E.A.R.)

F.E.A.R. First Encounter Assault Recon is a first-person shooter developed by Monolith Productions and published by Vivendi. It was released on October 18, 2005.

This is version 1.08.  Tested working on Windows 8.1 x64 (running in compatibility mode for Windows XP Service Pack 3).
Still a good looking game, nine years later.

Compatible trainer included, for those so inclined.
